               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340220-194-person1826">
                  THOMAS 
                  GRIFFITHS
               <interp inst="t18340220-194-person1826" type="surname" value="GRIFFITHS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340220-194-person1826" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18340220-194-person1826" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I employed these two men - they both lodged in one room - on the 26th of November the prisoner came down with a bundle - we had given him warning to leave - he washed himself and went away with the bundle without his breakfast - he left some cards of steel pens behind him - when I took him he asked the prosecutor what the articles were worth.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340220-194-person1827">
                  FRANCIS 
                  GRANEY
               <interp inst="t18340220-194-person1827" type="surname" value="GRANEY"></interp>
