                  </persName>
             (police-constable G 87). I took the prisoner - he said he would give 8s. to settle it, or if not, he did not care whether he got three months or seven years of it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The prosecutor wanted to settle with me; he asked me 1l., then 15s., and then 12s., and I offered him 8s.</p>
